Market insiders introduced that the "price guarantee agreement" also appeared in Nanjing in 2008.
In August of that year, Hengtang Xiyuan, a real estate project on Huangshan Road in Hexi, launched a "price guarantee plan" to attract homebuyers. The specific content was "The company solemnly promises that if the discount of the project expands within one year, the company will refund the difference to the old owners."
Subsequently, in April 2011, nine real estate projects in Nanjing also promised "price difference compensation" for some properties.
"The real estate market is warming up, and it needs a 'cardiotonic' at this time.
